&lt;p&gt;大功告成！每次你运行这个程序就可以得到一张随机的壁纸啦。&lt;/p&gt;</description><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">cty</dc:creator><pubDate>Sat, 05 Jul 2014 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>tag:cty12.github.io,2014-07-05:random_wallpaper_os_x.html</guid><category>Mac</category><category>OS X</category><category>python</category></item><item><title>Hello Pelican!</title><link>http://cty12.github.io/hello_pelican.html</link><description>&lt;h2&gt;This is my first blog post.&lt;/h2&gt;
